    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Craftsmen who specialize in staining glass, which is coloring glass by adding metallic oxides to the molten glass. To distinguish those who design and create the stained glass windows or other works, use "stained glass artists." For those who paint details on stained glass or othewise paint on glass, use "glass painters."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
